-- Regression test: an EXACTLY (expression) pattern mid-match must not derail
-- the pattern-match analysis. Expression patterns desugar to zero guards, so
-- the guard model used to treat `EXACTLY red` as a match-all and branded the
-- perfectly reachable later arms redundant — a blocking warning on valid,
-- total code. The analysis now stands down for CONSIDERs containing literal
-- or expression patterns (they carry no exhaustiveness guarantee), so this
-- file must typecheck clean and evaluate.
DECLARE Color IS ONE OF red, green, blue

GIVEN c IS A Color
GIVETH A NUMBER
f c MEANS
  CONSIDER c
  WHEN EXACTLY red THEN 1
  WHEN green THEN 2
  WHEN blue THEN 3

#EVAL f green
#EVAL f red
